#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn7.19"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn7.19:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 7 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 7 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn7.19:0.2"
msgid "2. Upāsakavagga "
msgstr "2. Lay Followers "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn7.19:0.3"
msgid "19. Mātuposakasutta "
msgstr "19. The Brahmin Who Provided for His Mother "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts1ed1.182, pts2ed1.391, sc1
msgctxt "sn7.19:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ. "
msgstr "At Sāvatthī. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn7.19:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho mātuposako brāhmaṇo yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavatā saddhiṃ sammodi. "
msgstr "Then a brahmin who provided for his mother went up to the Buddha, and exchanged greetings with him. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn7.19:1.3"
msgid "Sammodanīyaṃ kathaṃ sāraṇīyaṃ vītisāretvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho mātuposako brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "When the greetings and polite conversation were over, he sat down to one side and said to the Buddha, "

msgctxt "sn7.19:1.4"
msgid "“ahañhi, bho gotama, dhammena bhikkhaṃ pariyesāmi, dhammena bhikkhaṃ pariyesitvā mātāpitaro posemi. "
msgstr "“Master Gotama, I seek alms by legitimate means, which I use to provide for my mother and father. "

msgctxt "sn7.19:1.5"
msgid "Kaccāhaṃ, bho gotama, evaṅkārī kiccakārī homī”ti? "
msgstr "In doing so, am I doing my duty?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn7.19:1.6"
msgid "“Taggha tvaṃ, brāhmaṇa, evaṅkārī kiccakārī hosi. "
msgstr "“Indeed, brahmin, in so doing you are doing your duty. "

msgctxt "sn7.19:1.7"
msgid "Yo kho, brāhmaṇa, dhammena bhikkhaṃ pariyesati, dhammena bhikkhaṃ pariyesitvā mātāpitaro poseti, bahuṃ so puññaṃ pasavatīti. "
msgstr "Whoever seeks alms by legitimate means, and uses them to provide for their mother and father makes much merit. "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn7.19:2.1"
msgid "Yo mātaraṃ pitaraṃ vā, "
msgstr "A mortal provides for their mother "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn7.19:2.2"
msgid "macco dhammena posati; "
msgstr "and father by legitimate means; "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn7.19:2.3"
msgid "Tāya naṃ pāricariyāya, "
msgstr "because they look after "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn7.19:2.4"
msgid "mātāpitūsu paṇḍitā; "
msgstr "their parents like this, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn7.19:2.5"
msgid "Idheva naṃ pasaṃsanti, "
msgstr "they’re praised in this life by the astute, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "sn7.19:2.6"
msgid "pecca sagge pamodatī”ti. "
msgstr "and they depart to rejoice in heaven.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p>
#. REF: pts2ed1.392, sc3
msgctxt "sn7.19:3.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, mātuposako brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "When he said this, the brahmin who provided for his mother said to the Buddha, "

msgctxt "sn7.19:3.2"
msgid "“abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama, abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama … pe … "
msgstr "“Excellent, Master Gotama! Excellent! … "

msgctxt "sn7.19:3.3"
msgid "upāsakaṃ maṃ bhavaṃ gotamo dhāretu ajjatagge pāṇupetaṃ saraṇaṃ gatan”ti. "
msgstr "From this day forth, may Master Gotama remember me as a lay follower who has gone for refuge for life.”"

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
